{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ed062abda4","title":"关于重新印发毛泽东在七千人大会上讲话的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"670799fe22","index":0,"year":1966,"month":2,"day":6,"articleId":"ed062abda4"}],"tags":[{"id":"66d645281f","name":"准备和成因","type":"主题"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"afdf5cd1a7","name":"重要会议","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ea37adcd03","type":"title","text":"关于重新印发毛泽东在七千人大会上讲话的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ed062abda4"},{"id":"5f1e0f08f8","type":"paragraph","text":"彭真同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ed062abda4"},{"id":"ad0c132092","type":"paragraph","text":"请商在京常委及康生、定一、伯达诸同志，修改一遍，并考虑是否应中南局的要求印发给县、团级同志看（只发中南局，作为试点，别地不发。）看来此问题很大，要真正实现民主集中制，是要经过认真的教育、试点和推广，并经过长期反复进行，才能实现的，否则在大多数同志当中，始终不过是一句空话。王任重同志的修改是好的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ed062abda4"}],"page":{"id":"736ef9e817","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ed062abda4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}